data.text: @Charlie_Senack Thanks, Charlie. This is no fun.
@lisakirbie Oh no! Feel better soon! It seems it’s really going around this year!
@lisakirbie The best dogs, we had ayellow Lewis and a black Brewis said like bruise

@YYZemily Totally. We just thought my grandson picked up a tummy bug at school and didn’t think anything else about it 🥴. I was able to work today but I was looking pretty grey on a couple of zoom calls.
@JennJefferys Thanks Jenn. I’m not eating yet and I have lots of ginger ale to at least get some calories into me. 💛

@lisakirbie I hope you're feeling better now. You are not alone in trying to prevent Covid and was struck by another virus. It looks like things might be slowly getting back to normal. So many viruses have not been around as everyone has been wearing masks, etc.
@lisakirbie Been there, also thanks to a grandson. Hope you are better soon. It is nasty
@lisakirbie Very sorry to hear about this. Hope you feel better soon.
@lisakirbie I’m glad you’ve turned the corner … take the time to come back …occasionally it comes back in a second wave … we’ll be waiting 😊
@helenheller Was feeling off most of yesterday afternoon and then wham! It’s awful. Thanks for checking in, Helen. 💛
